{{!--
  WORK-PROJECTS SECTION
  Experimental/smaller work only — the featured set now lives exclusively
  in about-projects.hbs's varied grid; this section used to ALSO show the
  same tag:featured posts in its own "Real products..." block above this
  one, duplicating that content back-to-back on the Work page. Removed
  that block, leaving just the experimental listing, on a 3-per-row grid
  (see .posts-grid-cards in posts-tabs-grid.css).

  NOTE: deliberately does NOT filter on featured:true (Ghost's native
  "feature this post" toggle) — that flag curates the HOMEPAGE teaser
  (posts-tabs.hbs/posts-tabs-grid.hbs), a handpicked subset. tag:experimental
  is a separate custom tag, unrelated to the featured:true flag despite the
  name overlap.
--}}
<section class="statement-slide" style="min-height: 10vh; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 20vh;">
  <div class="statement-container">
    <h2 class="statement-heading">The Lab</h2>
    <h5 class="statement-description">Pitches, smaller projects, and explorations.</h5>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="work-projects-section">
  <div class="container">

    
    <div class="posts-grid-cards">
      {{#get "posts" filter="tag:hash-work+tag:experimental" limit="100" include="tags,authors"}}
        {{#foreach posts}}
          {{> post-card-grid first=@first}}
        {{/foreach}}
      {{/get}}
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

{{!-- posts-tabs-grid.js populates .grid-card-category/-title/-testimonial/
      etc. per card via a per-post metadata fetch. No <script> tag here —
      work-projects.hbs is only ever rendered from work.hbs, always right
      after about-projects.hbs, whose own script tag already covers this
      page. A second copy here executed the whole file twice (repeated
      <script src> tags aren't deduped by the browser), which broke the
      first grid-card's eager metadata fetch that page-transition.js's
      landing-animation gate depends on — see posts-tabs-grid.js's own
      window.__postsTabsGridInitialized guard for the full explanation. --}}

